Title: Object: Fuite en Egypte
Series: Galerie du Palais Royal
Description: The Flight into Egypt; landscape with the Virgin and Christ on a donkey in lower right, preceded by St Joseph and followed by two putti, a water-mill and bridge at left; with engraved text below, within decorative frame; after Hans Bol. c.1786-1807 Etching and engraving
Curator's comments: From 'Galerie du Palais Royal', see 1837,0408.317 for comment.
